metadata.name: I Finally Feel Free
metadata.description:
Bounded by my environment and pre-determined choices, I have struggled to free myself. Caught by the restrictions of time, I have searched for answers. Life experiences tied me down as I looked out to the sky. I've slowly become comfortable with who I am. 

It is now time to let go of my pain. I can't let it hold me back anymore. I have already strayed too far. I can now be myself and show the world who I am. 

I Finally Feel Free
